.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: white, purple, pink, emerald, turquise
There are 5 different nationalities: argentine, egyptian, french, pakistani, british
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, oliveros, siglo, swisher, chaman
There are 5 different favourite beverages: iced-soy-almond-milk, soy-almond-milk, almond-milk, mirinda, hot-chocolate
5 different pets are kept: fish, frog, bird, ferret, cat

1. the argentine is the person who likes white
2. the egyptian is the owner of the fish
3. the person drinking iced-soy-almond-milk is the person who likes purple
4. the french is the person drinking soy-almond-milk
5. the person who likes purple is to the right of the person who likes pink
6. the fonseca-smoker is the owner of the cat
7. the oliveros-smoker is the person who likes emerald
8. the person drinking almond-milk is in the middle
9. the pakistani is on the far left
10. the siglo-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the frog
11. the oliveros-smoker is to the left or right of the owner of the ferret
12. the swisher-smoker is the person drinking mirinda
13. the british is the chaman-smoker
14. the pakistani is to the left or right of the person who likes turquise

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Nationality	|   pakistani	|    french	|     argentine	|    egyptian	|    british	|
| Color		|    emerald	|      turquise	|      white	|     pink	|     purple	|
| Beverage	|     hot-chocolate	|      soy-almond-milk	|      almond-milk	| mirinda	|     iced-soy-almond-milk	|
| Cigar		|     oliveros	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| swisher	|   parliament	|
| Pet		|     frog	|     ferret	|     cat	|     fish	|     bird	|
